snippet.title: Family - Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Download at: https://owl-skip.itch.io/family
Soundtrack at: https://familygame.bandcamp.com/releases

Family is a puzzle game, based around a forgotten 80s indie music scene.

Discover the strange and wonderful music of long-lost bands, while uncovering their stories.

A tale of love, inspiration, pain, drama and jangly guitars. Made with Love.

This game is dedicated to the member of the London Pop Scene (1985-95).

We would like to thank its members for their cooperation and support.
